{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, YOLOX, Faster R-CNN and RetinaNet were all implemented with PyTorch 1.10.1.",
    "All training, validation, and test procedures were conducted on eight NVIDIA RTX 2080Ti graphics processing units (GPUs).",
    "Five validations were performed in our study.",
    "First, 5-fold cross-validation was performed on the CXR-AL14 dataset, and the five models were further tested on the held-out test dataset.",
    "Second, the held-out test dataset was used to evaluate the general performance of the YOLOX model."
  ]
}